Package Controller.Phases

Class EndGamePhase

java.lang.Object
Controller.Phases.Phase
Controller.Phases.EndGamePhase
public class EndGamePhase extends Phase
Represents the end game phase in the game. This phase allows players to view the game map, but no further editing or gameplay actions are allowed. All editing and gameplay commands result in an "Invalid command" message during this phase.
